description.content:
## WebSocket: Orders Real-Time Updates

Connect to receive real-time order notifications and status updates.

**URL:** `ws://localhost:8000/ws/orders/`

### Authentication

Uses Django session/auth middleware. Must be authenticated.

### Client Messages

**Subscribe to order updates:**
```json
{
  "action": "subscribe_order",
  "order_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
}
```

**Unsubscribe from order:**
```json
{
  "action": "unsubscribe_order",
  "order_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
}
```

### Server Messages

**New notification:**
```json
{
  "type": "notification",
  "data": {
    "notification_type": "order_accepted",
    "order_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
    "message": "Your order has been accepted.",
    "created_at": "2024-01-15T10:05:00Z"
  }
}
```

**Status update:**
```json
{
  "type": "status_update",
  "data": {
    "order_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
    "status": "accepted",
    "updated_at": "2024-01-15T10:05:00Z",
    "estimated_ready_time": "2024-01-15T10:35:00Z"
  }
}
```

**New order (chef only):**
```json
{
  "type": "new_order",
  "data": {
    "order_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
    "customer_name": "John Doe",
    "total_amount": "35.98",
    "items_count": 2,
    "message": "New order from John Doe",
    "created_at": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

**Subscription confirmed:**
```json
{
  "type": "subscribed",
  "order_id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
}
```

### JavaScript Example

```javascript
const ws = new WebSocket('ws://localhost:8000/ws/orders/');

ws.onopen = () => {
  console.log('Connected');
  ws.send(JSON.stringify({
    action: 'subscribe_order',
    order_id: '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
  }));
};

ws.onmessage = (event) => {
  const message = JSON.parse(event.data);
  console.log(message.type, message.data);
};
```

### Groups

| Group | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `user_{user_id}` | Personal notifications |
| `order_{order_id}` | Order-specific status updates |
